STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Dylan Daniel MILLARD, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0367 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Dylan Millard appeals the sentence imposed on his conviction for possession of marijuana with intent to deliver. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
